                    <p>The expected duration uses the PERT formula: <strong>E = (O + 4M + P) / 6</strong></p>
                    <p><strong>Example:</strong> If a feature might take 2 days (optimistic), probably 5 days (most likely), or 10 days (pessimistic):</p>
